          "sceneY": 250,
          "script": "const SPEED = 80;\n\nif (!state.goombaDir) state.goombaDir = {};\nlet id = self.name || 'unknown';\nif (!state.goombaDir[id]) state.goombaDir[id] = -1;\n\n// Patrol movement\nself.x += SPEED * state.goombaDir[id] * dt;\n\n// Bounce at edges\nif (self.x < -400) state.goombaDir[id] = 1;\nif (self.x > 400) state.goombaDir[id] = -1;\n"
